sequenceDiagram
    participant CR as Celery Worker<br/>(PipelineRunner)
    participant DB as PostgreSQL<br/>(ExecutionStep)
    participant MC as mojo-compute<br/>HTTP API
    participant S3 as S3 / RustFS

    Note over CR: step_type == "MOJO" detected

    CR->>DB: UPDATE ExecutionStep<br/>status=RUNNING, started_at=now

    CR->>MC: POST /execute<br/>{"run_id", "script", "s3_input", "s3_output"}

    MC->>S3: GET s3_input (Parquet)
    S3-->>MC: input data

    Note over MC: Execute Mojo script<br/>fn main() raises

    MC->>S3: PUT s3_output (Parquet)<br/>PUT s3_output/result.json
    S3-->>MC: 200 OK

    MC-->>CR: 200 {"status": "ok",<br/>"row_count": N, "duration_ms": N}

    CR->>DB: UPDATE ExecutionStep<br/>status=COMPLETED, completed_at=now

    Note over CR: Continue to next step

    alt Mojo script error
        MC-->>CR: 200 {"status": "error",<br/>"message": "..."}
        CR->>DB: UPDATE ExecutionStep<br/>status=FAILED, error_message=message
        CR->>CR: raise RuntimeError
    end

    alt mojo-compute unreachable
        MC-->>CR: Connection error / timeout
        CR->>DB: UPDATE ExecutionStep<br/>status=FAILED, error_message=connection error
        CR->>CR: raise RuntimeError
    end
